⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Semyon Marmeladov
node CRP · CRP · ⟦Semyon Marmeladov:CRP:e97dc9⟧

WHO   — Semyon Marmeladov — the drunkard · the confession in the tavern
WHAT  — The voice of abject self-knowledge: he drinks his family into ruin, knows it, and begs for a God who pities even the swine.
WHERE — CRP · Crime and Punishment  Framework inputs: Crime and Punishment (Dostoevsky, 1866)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the novel grounds its philosophy in real, crushing poverty — and in a man who needs mercy precisely because he deserves none.
HOW   — By the bottle, by Sonya's sacrifice that he cannot stop exploiting, and by a death under a carriage's wheels.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I am a swine, and I drink even my daughter's shame — but will He not pity us too, the ones who pity themselves least?

spoken token : daex-mend-moth   ·   hex : e97dc9
